            "description": "Calls DeepSeek via backend. Requires valid `AI_API_KEY` in server `.env`.\n\n**Body fields:**\n- `ingredients` (required): string[]\n- `tools` (optional): string[]\n- `calorieLimit` (optional): number — whole dish, all servings\n- `servings` (optional): positive integer\n\nReturns 201 with saved recipe or 502 on AI failure."
